## 5️⃣ Fragments для переиспользования

### Создание fragments

**✅ ПРАВИЛЬНО - DRY principle:**

```typescript
// lib/graphql/fragments/doctor.ts
import { gql } from '@apollo/client';

export const DOCTOR_CARD_FRAGMENT = gql`
  fragment DoctorCard on Doctor {
    id
    title
    slug
    doctorFields {
      specialty
      experience
      rating
      avatar {
        sourceUrl
        mediaDetails {
          width
          height
        }
      }
    }
  }
`;

export const DOCTOR_FULL_FRAGMENT = gql`
  fragment DoctorFull on Doctor {
    ...DoctorCard
    content
    doctorFields {
      bio
      education
      certifications
      clinics {
        ... on Clinic {
          id
          title
        }
      }
    }
  }
  ${DOCTOR_CARD_FRAGMENT}
`;
```

### Использование fragments

**✅ ПРАВИЛЬНО:**

```typescript
import { DOCTOR_CARD_FRAGMENT } from '@/lib/graphql/fragments/doctor';

const GET_DOCTORS = gql`
  query GetDoctors {
    doctors(first: 50) {
      edges {
        node {
          ...DoctorCard
        }
      }
    }
  }
  ${DOCTOR_CARD_FRAGMENT}
`;
```

